  "scope_caveats": [
    "(s1) Materials Project values are DFT-computed (PBE-GGA), NOT experimentally measured. Band gaps are systematically underestimated by 30-50% (DFT gap problem); formation energies have \u00b10.1 eV/atom error bars; lattice constants are typically +1-3% overestimated.",
    "(s2) Debye temperature and electron-phonon coupling (\u03bb, \u03c9_log, \u03bc*) are NOT exposed in standard MP summary endpoints \u2014 Tier 1 sim_adapter must ingest these from a separate source (phonon DB / Allen-Dynes Table I / first-principles paper). MP rows have debye_temp_K=null by design.",
    "(s3) Tc prediction is NOT in MP. This adapter ingests *structural and electronic* data only. Tc inference requires \u03bb + \u03c9_log + \u03bc* fed into McMillan/Allen-Dynes via sim_adapter, or a full Eliashberg solve (hexa-native-absent).",
